title: Part 2: Your Greater Is Coming Special
itunes:title: Part 2: Your Greater Is Coming Special
description:
In part 2 of the Your Greater is Coming Special, Joel, Victoria, and friends continue the discussion of Joel’s new book Your Greater Is Coming. God is working behind the scene even when we don’t see anything happen. Don’t let the enemy use his never lies, because your greater is coming.

 

God is setting you up for something magnificent. Request your copy of Your Greater is Coming today. https://www.JoelOsteen.com/greater?sourcecode=2210JWBP&utm_campaign=2210&utm_medium=web&utm_source=podcast&utm_term=onsale

 

 

Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope
